Centos安装Tengine步骤

1.wget http://tengine.taobao.org/download/tengine-2.2.0.tar.gz

2.tar -zxvf tengine-2.2.0.tar.gz

3.检查Tengine安装依赖库
yum install gcc-c++  
yum -y install pcre pcre-devel  
yum -y install zlib zlib-devel  
yum -y install openssl openssl-devel

4.输入安装命令并指定安装路径 ./configure --prefix=/soft/nginx

5.编译和安装make，make install

6.进入安装，目前启动sbin/nginx,浏览器输入本机公网地址。看到欢迎页面即表示安装成功

7.配置nginx.conf
